----------------------------------------
DOCKER
----------------------------------------
1. Working with Docker CLI Commands (Using Redis)
Step 1: Pull Redis image
docker pull redis

Step 2: Run Redis container
docker run --name my-redis -d redis

Step 3: Check running containers
docker ps

Step 4: Access Redis CLI
docker exec -it my-redis redis-cli


Example inside Redis:

SET name "Alice"
GET name
exit

Step 5: Stop container
docker stop my-redis

Step 6: Start container
docker start my-redis

Step 7: Remove container
docker rm my-redis

Step 8: Remove image
docker rmi redis

2. Working with Dockerfile
Step 1: Create project folder

Windows:

cd /c/DockerProjects/Redis


Mac/Linux:

mkdir ~/DockerProjects/Redis
cd ~/DockerProjects/Redis

Step 2: Create Dockerfile

Content:

FROM redis:latest
CMD ["redis-server"]

Docker Commands (Step-by-Step)
1. Build image
docker build -t redisnew .

2. Run container
docker run --name myredisnew -d redisnew

3. List running containers
docker ps

4. Stop container
docker stop myredisnew

5. Login to DockerHub
docker login

6. Show all containers
docker ps -a

7. Commit container to image
docker commit <container_id> budarajumadhurika/redis1

8. List images
docker images

9. Push image to DockerHub
docker push budarajumadhurika/redis1

10. Remove container
docker rm <container_id>

11. Remove image
docker rmi budarajumadhurika/redis1

12. Again list all containers
docker ps -a

13. Logout
docker logout

14. Pull uploaded image
docker pull budarajumadhurika/redis1

15. Run container from pulled image
docker run --name myredis -d budarajumadhurika/redis1

16. Enter Redis CLI
docker exec -it myredis redis-cli


Commands:

SET name "Abcdef"
GET name
exit

17. List containers
docker ps -a

18. Stop container
docker stop myredis

19. Remove container
docker rm <container_id>

20. List images
docker images

21. Remove image
docker rmi budarajumadhurika/redis1

GROOVY SCRIPT
-------------
pipeline {
    agent any

    tools {
        maven 'MAVEN-HOME'      // Jenkins → Global Tools → Maven name
    }

    stages {

        stage('Clone Repository') {
            steps {
                git branch: 'main',
                    url: 'https://github.com/your/repo.git'
            }
        }

        stage('Maven Clean') {
            steps {
                sh 'mvn clean'
            }
        }

        stage('Maven Install') {
            steps {
                sh 'mvn install'
            }
        }

        stage('Maven Test') {
            steps {
                sh 'mvn test'
            }
        }
    }
}
